reviews.text: The dim sum was good but just average. Easy to read menu though!

From dumplings to steamed buns, there's a huge variety of delicious dimsum. You'll find all the classics and plenty more at this restaurant. The prices are also very fair, and you can get some pretty good deals for some pretty great dimsum dishes.
Tasty dim sum at a very decent price. A basic place so ideal for a quick bite.
Loved all the fresh food 🍲 they offer
Dimsum not bad, machang or sticky fried rice really good. Siomai and chicken feet are worth ordering. Prices are reasonable also. Highly recommended.
